<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Patiently" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Patiently,</orth> 1) with calm endurance in suffering: <bibl n="shak. luc 1641" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1641</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 5.3.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. V, 3, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 2.3.20" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. II, 3, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 3.2.79" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 79</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 1.2.86" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 2, 86</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 5.1.36" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 1, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.78" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 9, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.5.12" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 5, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.300" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 300</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.5.118" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. III, 5, 118</bibl>.<lb />2) calmly, tranquilly: <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.140" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 140</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 2.7.61" default="NO" valid="yes">As II, 7, 61</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.0" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV Chor.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.156" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 156</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 5.9.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 9, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.36" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 6, 36</bibl>.
<lb />3) with indulgence: <cit><quote>we beg your hearing p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.161" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 161</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>good heavens, hear p. my purpose,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 5.1.22" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 1, 22</bibl></cit>.
